```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Source as Data Source
    participant Glue as Glue ETL
    participant S3 as S3 Lakehouse
    participant Catalog as Data Catalog
    participant LF as Lake Formation
    participant Athena as Athena
    participant User as Analyst

    Source->>Glue: Trigger ETL job
    Glue->>S3: Read raw data (Bronze)
    Glue->>Glue: Transform & validate
    Glue->>S3: Write cleaned data (Silver)
    Glue->>Catalog: Update schema
    
    Note over Glue,S3: Delta Lake ACID transaction
    
    Glue->>S3: Write curated data (Gold)
    Glue->>Catalog: Register table
    Catalog->>LF: Apply permissions

    User->>Athena: Submit query
    Athena->>LF: Check permissions
    LF-->>Athena: Authorized
    Athena->>S3: Scan Delta table
    S3-->>Athena: Return data
    Athena-->>User: Query results
```
